[[Schwa]] {{IPA|[<U+0259>]}} occurs only in [[stress (linguistics)|unstressed]] [[syllable]]s. [[Vowel length]] is predictable:
*Unstressed vowels are short.
*Stressed vowels in closed syllables (those with a [[syllable coda|coda]]) are:
*:long before {{IPA|/r/}}
*:short elsewhere
*Stressed vowels in open syllables are:
*:short before [[voiceless consonant]]s
*:long elsewhere

