==Some common expressions==
*''Allegra.'' <U+2013> Hello or welcome
*''Co vai?'' <U+2013> How are you?
*''Fa plaschair.'' <U+2013> Pleased to meet you.
*''Bun di.'' <U+2013> Good morning.
*''Buna saira.'' <U+2013> Good evening.
*''Buna notg.'' <U+2013> Good night.
*''A revair.'' <U+2013> Goodbye.
*''A pli tard.'' <U+2013> See you later.
*''Perstgisai.'' <U+2013> I beg your pardon.
*''I ma displascha.'' <U+2013> I'm sorry.
*''Perdunai.'' <U+2013> Excuse me.
*''Per plaschair.'' <U+2013> Please.
*''Grazia fitg.'' <U+2013> Thank you very much.
*''Anzi.'' <U+2013> You're welcome.
*''Gratulazions.'' <U+2013> Congratulations.
*''Bun cletg.'' <U+2013> Good luck.
*''Ils quants <U+00E8> oz?'' <U+2013> What's the date today?
*''Quants onns has ti?'' <U+2013> How old are you?
*''Viva!'' <U+2013> Cheers!

